text2 CODE 0 CD6 CD6 18 1 2
text3 CODE 0 C0C C0C 52 1 2
text4 CODE 0 CEE CEE 12 1 2
text5 CODE 0 C5E C5E 34 1 2
text6 CODE 0 C92 C92 2A 1 2
